Title: Invisibles
Writer: Marion Doussot (collaboration), Claire Lajeunie (based on the book), Claire Lajeunie (collaboration), Louis-Julien Petit (screenplay)
Actors: Patricia Mouchon, Khoukha Boukherbache, Bérangère Toural, Patricia Guery
Plot: Following a municipal decision, Envol, SDF Women's Shelter, will close. There are only three months left for social workers to reintegrate at any cost the women they care for: falsification...
